Trivia is an online social game, currently a very basic proof of concept.
Currently, there is no SSO, should be FB connect later.

Users have to find the right answer to questions asked by other users.

Users start with 200 points.
Asking a question costs 50 points.
Answering a question give you 100 points.

Questions should have a timeout.
Asker also get 100 points if the question is answered before the timeout.